&lt;p&gt;This makes negligible difference to the smaller tables, but gives a ~10% boost for orders (50.8Gb ORC) and lineitem (224.5Gb ORC).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The optimization does not benefit the sorted string columns, because for every row read there&apos;s a data-copy to populate either the minimum or maximum in the column statistics section (Strings are immutable, Text is Writable).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
